----------------------------------------------------------
|0 |DELETE            |            |2       |26          |
|1 |└─TABLE RANGE SCAN|t1(t1_idx_1)|2       |10          |
==========================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output(nil), filter(nil)
      table_columns([{t1: ({t1: (t1.c1, t1.c2, t1.c3)})}])
  1 - output([t1.c1], [t1.c2], [t1.c3], [t1.TRANS_DEBUG_INFO]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([t1.c1], [t1.c2], [t1.c3]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=true, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([t1.c3], [t1.c1]), range(1,MAX ; MAX,MAX), 
